    <keyword>TOPT-ENVIR</keyword>
    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies a mechanism for passing environment information between a telnet client and server.  Use of this mechanism enables a telnet user to propagate configuration information to a remote host when connecting. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
